  {
    "id": "09-that-s-a-good-looking-dwarf_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "The party investigated reports of a raging bulas near mines. After slaying the creature and trading its pelt for magic boots, Mollywop's alarm sent them to a fisherman's hut where a large creature erupted from the river during Market Day.",
