      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "08-devil-spawn_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "The party plunged into the hidden cellar beneath the Adsuren Center determined to root out the Cult of the Immured and shatter their blood rituals before more townsfolk fell victim. They carved through chanting cultists in a gore-slicked chamber only to unmask the respected Intendant Eyovar Dunajor as the fiendish summoner Karranok. The interrupted rite summoned the succubus Aeolenne who promptly declared Zephyra her daughter, sparking a chaotic battle. Though the demoness escaped, the party dismantled the cult, delivered justice to its traitor, and emerged victorious with treasures, revelations, and fresh resolve to press on into the mines.",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "7",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "08-devil-spawn_recording_1",
    "type": "media-player",
