  {
    "id": "04-putrid_title",
    "type": "header",
    "props": {
      "title": "04 - Putrid",
      "color": "gold",
      "size": "md",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "22",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "04-putrid_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "Returning to Adsuren, the group sought answers about the growing corruption tied to stolen hearts and the ritual they had uncovered in the swamp. After consulting Mollywop, they learned the heart was human, bound by necromancy and fiendish magic, and likely created by a hidden group operating within the town itself. Investigating the graveyard, they confirmed their fears when an unearthed body missing its heart rose as an undead attacker. After destroying it, they were working with the early signs of a cult working in secret among Adsuren's people. Spreading out for more information led to an untimely attack upon Kenton, with the party unaware.",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "23",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "04-putrid_recording_1",
