    }
  },
  {
    "id": "02-mollywop-to-sapcutt_title",
    "type": "header",
    "props": {
      "title": "02 - Mollywop to Sapcutt",
      "color": "gold",
      "size": "md",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "30",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "02-mollywop-to-sapcutt_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "After saving Adsuren's well, the party sought to understand the darker magic behind the corruption and welcomed a new companion, Lila, into their ranks. They destroyed the tainted heart under holy blessing and set out to consult Mollywop the Magnificent for deeper insight. In exchange for her help, they agreed to investigate the disappearance of the Sapcutt family and traveled into the swampy lowlands beyond the river. What began as a warm welcome at the Sapcutt ranch ended in betrayal, as the party was drugged during dinner and dropped through a hidden pit beneath the house.",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "31",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
