    }
  },
  {
    "id": "01-we-meet_title",
    "type": "header",
    "props": {
      "title": "01 - We Meet",
      "color": "gold",
      "size": "md",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "34",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "01-we-meet_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "In their first meeting in Adsuren, the newly formed party was drawn together by a sudden crisis when a villager collapsed after drinking from the town well. What began as a chance encounter quickly became a shared purpose as they set out to discover the source of the poisoning threatening the village. Their investigation led them beneath the settlement, where they fought through restless undead and uncovered a corrupted underground stream. By destroying the unnatural growth tainting the water and recovering its disturbing remnants, the party saved the well and prevented further harm, while realizing their brief alliance had become something more permanent.",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "35",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
